{"tid":2339896,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"9 歲仔為買 Apple Watch 創業　自製香薰蠟燭年賺過 10 萬","createTime":"2020-12-25T04:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T04:13:04.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8fb8bf41056866b03f4271bda8f2e91c864dc4","tid":2339896,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2835000/2836707/cover_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2835000%2F2836707%2Fcover_1024.jpg&h=bb5cf0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信幾乎每位家長都必定試過被孩子要求買玩具。澳洲一位 9 歲小朋友拜託媽媽買 Apple Watch 給他，卻遭到拒絕。於是「化悲憤為力量」，為了獲得 Apple Watch，他開始自製香薰蠟燭售賣，一年間便賺得約 12 萬港幣。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲一位小朋友 Tadyn Flood 年僅 9 歲，便有一門販賣香薰蠟燭的生意，而其創業動力竟然是源自於媽媽不買 Apple Watch，於是決心自己賺錢去買「心頭好」。Tadyn 透過 YouTube 上的教學影片，自學製作手工香薰蠟燭，製成後將其賣給親朋好友，後來生意更越做越大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2835000/2836707/candle1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2835000%2F2836707%2Fcandle1_600.jpg&h=fe68de4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTadyn 的媽媽會載他到週末市集上擺檔，一支蠟燭賣約 10 至 15 美元，每個星期能賣出超過 300 美元的蠟燭，在短短一年內便賺得 1.5 萬美元（約 11.7 萬港元）。除了成功買到夢寐以求的 Apple Watch 以外，還可以定期儲蓄，甚至會抽出部分收益捐給弱勢社群。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2835000/2836707/candle2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2835000%2F2836707%2Fcandle2_600.jpg&h=89f60cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTadyn 終於憑自己的力量買到 Apple Watch！<br />\n<br />\nTadyn 的媽媽分享，創業經歷對 Tadyn 學習同樣有幫助，他從前在學業上遇到的難題，都在學懂如何計算那些生意收益後迎刃而解。不過，創業亦為這位 9 歲的小朋友帶來麻煩，由於每次存款到銀行的金額太多，安全風險高，Tadyn 的學校銀行帳戶已遭到停用。這也驅使 Tadyn 申請一個銀行帳戶，並學習如何配合 Apple Watch 管理，亦學會了用信用卡支付來理財。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2835000/2836707/39F9F2AF00000578-3896266-Tadyn_s_mother_Jo_Ann_Flood_said_the_business_has_even_given_a_b-a-17_1478068123401_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2835000%2F2836707%2F39F9F2AF00000578-3896266-Tadyn_s_mother_Jo_Ann_Flood_said_the_business_has_even_given_a_b-a-17_1478068123401_600.jpg&h=9d585070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n創業對 Tadyn 的學業已亦有幫助。"},{"pid":"7ee4f2bc6702e9b6e40ce36145ed9a136578a11e","tid":2339896,"uid":13219,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"老母：幫你儲住錢先，大個比返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3099d7a90e663b5f53d023faf3927b0175598819","tid":2339896,"uid":211323,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"如果係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊洗要自己搵錢買apple watch <br />\n叫聲爹哋就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c27c2a08acefff937c870a172459e20bd77bfd7","tid":2339896,"uid":35468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"sq 喺美國係咪已經好流行？<br />\n見個細路著住sq 嘅T-shirt <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc80ca5bd3f678363d15061e07bd381a6e660926","tid":2339896,"uid":69872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8c27c2a08acefff937c870a172459e20bd77bfd7","tid":2339896,"uid":35468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"sq 喺美國係咪已經好流行？<br />\n見個細路著住sq 嘅T-shirt <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T05:22:30.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi